            <scopecontent id="aspace_fea0865b8c20b540eeb720a16232eec2">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The correspondence between the members of the committee involved issues such as placement of the memorial, sketches for its completion and the inscription. Much discussion is given over to the placement and wording of the inscription, especially concerning the title of the War. The miscellaneous correspondence is involved mostly with the researching of names, both North and South, for the memorial.</p>
            </scopecontent>
